 if more changes are needed (team)</span></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Kada će biti detaljno ažuriranje na timskom sastanku?</p>","answers":[{"answer":"<p>Svako jutro u 3 ujutru.</p>","feedback":"<p>To opisuje stari raspored, nije novi plan.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Samo je ponedeljak</p>","feedback":"<p>Ponedeljak nije dan odabran za duboke sastanke.</p>","audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Utorak i četvrtak u 3 ujutro.</p>","feedback":null,"audioId":null},{"answer":"<p>Kraj svakog dana</p>","feedback":"<p>Sastanci su sada zakazani za ujutro na posebnom danu.</p>","audioId":null}],"solution":3}],"scene":null,"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","tests":[],"title":"Vežba 41","transcript":null,"translationPending":false,"videoId":null,"videoLocaleIds":null}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/#learn-about-adverbial-phrases","dashedName":"task-41","certification":"b1-english-for-developers","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"b1-english-for-developers","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"learn-about-adverbial-phrases","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-about-adverbial-phrases/task-42","prevChallengePath":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-about-adverbial-phrases/task-40","id":"680553835dc5f22e8000c791","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":19,"challengeFiles":[]}},"id":"/learn/b1-english-for-developers/learn-about-adverbial-phrases/task-41"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}